snippet.title: Best VGM 700 - Mega Man 2 - Intro Theme
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 66 - http://youtube.com/watch?v=vaJvNNWO_OQ
Best VGM 153 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HFKtYCcMWT4

Best VGM 914 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jXGaW3dKaHs

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Mega Man 2 (1989)
Intro Theme
Manami Matsumae, Yoshihiro Sakaguchi & Ogeretsu Kun
